title: How Amber Heard Got Caught Red-Handed in the Johnny Depp Trial

media:group.media:title: How Amber Heard Got Caught Red-Handed in the Johnny Depp Trial
media:group.media:description:
The Johnny Depp and Amber Heard trial allowed the public to peek behind the closed doors of two of Hollywood’s brightest stars. Nothing appeared to be off limits and every moment from the trial has been dissected under a microscope. The final verdict appears to have done little to change people’s stances. What has been left in the aftermath?
